SY: ...of India, in the Constituent Assembly of India.

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:35.480
Mataji, before She took up this message of spreading

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:39.520
Hindu philosophy and Hindu thoughts,

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:43.960
She was married in a very intellectually, prominent family

00:02:44.200 --> 00:02:51.079
and She was married to Shri C.P. Shrivastava.

00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:58.000
[Those of you] who know the post freedom leadership,

00:02:58.200 --> 00:03:00.600
among the IAS community,

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:03.080
very well-known some of the names,

00:03:03.320 --> 00:03:05.720
and Shri C.P. Shrivastava's name

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:09.200
was one of the most prominent names.

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:11.248
He had the distinction of being

00:03:11.449 --> 00:03:15.480
the principal private secretary to Shastriji,

00:03:15.720 --> 00:03:18.000
Shri Lal Bhahadur Shastri.

00:03:18.440 --> 00:03:21.579
And only now after seeing his name, I remember Mataji.

00:03:21.780 --> 00:03:24.480
When I was a secretary Government Teachers' Foundation

00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:27.400
and we had a conference in Delhi,

00:03:27.600 --> 00:03:29.920
when we were invited to Shastriji’s house,

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:33.009
it was Shrivastavaji who conducted the guests

00:03:33.210 --> 00:03:36.200
to the, to the house of Shastriji.

00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:39.654
And I have great pleasure that God creates situations,

00:03:39.855 --> 00:03:42.513
that we meet different people at different situation,

00:03:42.715 --> 00:03:45.680
just to prove that the world is so small.

00:03:45.880 --> 00:03:51.799
Shrivastavaji, after serving as a
distinguished person with Shastriji,

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:56.753
then he was transferred to the, to the

00:03:58.160 --> 00:04:02.079
to the Shipping Corporation of India,

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:03.920
where he was the secretary,

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:07.880
and later on he was with the United Nation Agency,

00:04:08.080 --> 00:04:12.240
in the form of International Maritime Agency.

00:04:12.440 --> 00:04:15.800
Now this is the background of this intellectual family.

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:19.600
As the holders of important positions in the government of India

00:04:19.800 --> 00:04:23.200
and in the International Assembly at the UNO,

00:04:23.400 --> 00:04:25.479
they must be coming in contact with

00:04:25.680 --> 00:04:28.960
highly prominent international personalities.

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:31.640
And Mataji among them all,

00:04:31.840 --> 00:04:34.520
instead of glorifying Herself,

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:37.600
in those positions of contacts and great places,

00:04:37.800 --> 00:04:41.680
Her bent of mind was towards spiritualism.

00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:43.960
And today [with the event], She lectures to us,

00:04:44.200 --> 00:04:48.760
when She tells us some of the mysteries of our teachings,

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:54.159
we will have the occasion of knowing Her more of the message.

00:04:54.920 --> 00:04:59.760
Born near Nagpur, at a place called Chinddwara.

00:04:59.960 --> 00:05:04.799
She is younger than me

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:10.600
and the glow of the charm of the spiritual world,

00:05:10.800 --> 00:05:12.720
as you see on Mataji’s face,

00:05:12.921 --> 00:05:17.121
it is a rare thing to find people so radiant invariably.

00:05:17.322 --> 00:05:21.002
And then She speaks to us [unclear].

