00:05:30.560 --> 00:05:32.200
You are in the program

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:35.640
and when the time comes we tell You, request You to come and speak.

00:05:35.840 --> 00:05:38.919
If You like to sit on the platform and speak.

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:42.680
Or You would like to stand? As You like.

00:05:45.480 --> 00:05:47.520
It is also our practice to let you know

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:49.440
as to what we have been doing

00:05:49.640 --> 00:05:54.360
during the month when we met you last and now.

