00:05:59.960 --> 00:06:03.599
and the High Commissioner invites the various organizations

00:06:03.800 --> 00:06:07.960
to plan and organize the 15-th of August program.

00:06:08.160 --> 00:06:11.240
We were invited there and we did a promise

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:15.840
that we will take part in whatever the activities are being done.

